Class StableCompoundEdit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openide.text.StableCompoundEdit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UndoableEdit

    public class StableCompoundEdit
extends Object
implements UndoableEdit
    Similar to Swing's CompoundEdit but guarantees stability of internal state even if undo()/redo() throws an exception.
